  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Tyre Development</h2>
  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Whichever track we're at, tyres always play a critical yet often misunderstood variable in the equation of performance.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Understanding your tyre operating window and how they degrade both mechanically and chemically as they age over a stint is the difference between being at the front of the grid, or the rear. In 2022 Wavey Dynamics formed a technical partnership with Thermolysis and Traction Research, the technology company specialised in developing advanced tyre modelling and characterisation techniques.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">This partnership allows us to:</p>
  <ul class="wd-list mb-8 space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
    <li>Bring you the benefits of high fidelity thermo-mechanical tyre models to include real-time prediction of thermal effects, wear effects and chemical degradation for their effect on performance</li>
    <li>Physically measure viscoelastic properties trackside to quantify thermal operating windows and degradation over a stint</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mb-10 leading-relaxed">With this partnership and the addition of this technology into our consulting services, we further close the gap between the simulated world and the measured world.</p>

  <p class="mb-10 leading-relaxed">Get in touch and we'll discuss how we can help you to the front of the grid.</p>

